data.description: Beautiful, Brick Home in the Estates of Keever Creek. Approx 4,000 sq ft of Living Space.  Lg In-ground, Heated, Salt-Water Pool w/ Expansive Stamped Concr Patio & Trex Deck Overlooking Warren County's Nature Preserve & Keever Trails. Gorgeous Gourmet Kit w/ SS Appl, Granite & Enormous Pantry is Open to Liv Rm w/ Cozy Gas FP & w/o to Deck. 1st Flr Study w/ French Doors. 2nd Flr Laundry & Loft. Abundance of Closet Space. Newly Finished Walk-Out LL is Ideal as a Mother-in-Law Suite and is Fully Equipped w/ Full Kit feat SS Appl, Fam Rm, Game Area, 5th Bed Rm & Full Ba. Oversized, 3 Car Garage. Conveniently Located Near Shopping, Restaurants & Access to Highways. This Incredible Home has it All!  Must See!
